s that is rarely found. The three heads respectively represent joy, sadness, and anger."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Watch out if Dodrio\u2019s three heads are looking in three separate directions. It\u2019s a sure sign that it is on its guard. Don\u2019t go near this Pok\u00e9mon if it\u2019s being wary\u2014it may decide to peck you."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Apparently, the heads aren\u2019t the only parts of the body that Dodrio has three of. It has three sets of hearts and lungs as well, so it is capable of running long distances without rest."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"One of Doduo\u2019s two heads splits to form a unique species. It runs close to 40 mph in prairies."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"One of Doduo\u2019s two heads splits to form a unique species. It runs close to 40 mph in prairies."}],"evo":{"name":"doduo","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"dodrio","level":1,"min_level":31,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/85.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/85.png","capture":45,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"attack":2},"forms":[]}